PrecisRegulations Amending the NATIONAL PARKS GARBAGE REGULATIONS by raising garbage collection fees in Jasper National Park by approximately 15%, by making the use of self-dumping garbage containers mandatory in six parks, and by making such other amendments as are required to make them consistent with the new Canada National Parks Act [Bill C-27].

precis:
Regulations Amending the NATIONAL PARKS GARBAGE REGULATIONS by raising
garbage collection fees in Jasper National Park by approximately 15%, by
making the use of self-dumping garbage containers mandatory in six parks,
and by making such other amendments as are required to make them consistent
with the new Canada National Parks Act [Bill C-27].
